            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Multi-Format Support</h3>
                <p>Upload PDF, DOCX, code files, or paste directly. Supports 40+ file types including .py, .js, .pdf, .docx.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M9 9h6M9 12h6M9 15h4"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Code Optimization</h3>
                <p>Auto-removes blank lines, reduces Python indentation 4→2 spaces, compacts JS braces — before rendering.</p>
            </article>
